# 🔐 Guarding Transactions with AI-Powered Credit Card Fraud Detection

AI-based system to detect fraudulent credit card transactions using a Random Forest model.

![Fraud Distribution](visuals/fraud_distribution.png)
![Feature Importance](visuals/feature_importance.png)

## 🚀 Features
- Machine Learning classification with Random Forest
- Interactive demo using Gradio
- Auto-generated visual insights (Seaborn, Matplotlib)
- Label Encoding for categorical inputs

## 🛠 How to Run

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python fraud_model.py       # Train the model and generate visualizations
python app.py               # Launch interactive prediction
